snippet.title: Hooked on Wood
snippet.description:
Hi, My name is Dennis, and I am from Hooked on Wood.
As a hobbyist woodworker, I started my youtube channel in 2019. I am interested in finding ways to improve my workshop, and as you watch my shop improvement playlist, you will discover that I try to search for new approaches to common problems. Sometimes, they are better, and sometimes they do not.  I try to inspire fellow woodworkers to look at different angles when creating a pleasant woodworking environment. 

China Tools series
I get a lot of excellent praise for my China tools series. Here I give In-depth reviews of woodworking products from China. Meanwhile, I tested a  lot of interesting products. On my website: www.hookedonwood.online you can find a ranking among these products. 
It can save you some money.

Thank you for watching my channel. I hope you will subscribe and join the club.
